This time Hellpeon was ready for a retaliation and moved both his 
legs by bringing them up a second before Ultimo reached where they 
were. Not wanting to waste any more energy hellpeon laughs as he 
looks down at Ultimo.

Hellpeon: "See you at the tournament fool."

And with those words Hellpeon speeds off towards the Oteybis, 
although now moving much slower due to the wounds.
